{{ja-kanjitab|めーとる|yomi=k}}
Borrowing from {{bor|ja|fr|sort=めえとる|mètre}}.<ref name="DJR"/>

The use of this kanji is attested in the {{w|Meiji period}} and is an example of {{ateji|sort=めえとる}}, shortened from {{bor|ja|cmn|sort=めえとる|米突|tr=mǐtū}}, see [[#Chinese|Chinese]] section above.

